        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>To <addressee>Miss E. Bomeisler</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Secy. Ladies' <add>?</add> Home Association.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dr Madam.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">It would afford me great pleasure to com-<lb/>ply with the request
                of the society you represent<lb/> to address them on <date>Tuesday the 12<hi
                        rend="sup">th</hi> of February</date><lb/> next, if it were in my power. But
                there is one<lb/> clause in the <add>?</add> “at the Portuguese Synagogue”<lb/>
                which is a ban to my compliance; as the cir-<lb/>cumstances which attended my
                connection<lb/> with the body <sic>worshipping</sic> therein would
                <del>make</del><lb/> evidently render it unbecoming for my <del>part</del> to<lb/>
                take part in any celebration or meeting held<lb/> in a building over which the
                president, <add>?</add><lb/> and members of the Portuguese congregation claim<lb/>
                and have the exclusive control. There is how-<lb/>ever the condition which if
                complied with will<lb/> enable me to do so as I am requested, that is<lb/> if a
                notice from the President and Adjuntor<add>?</add><lb/> or of a majority of them at
                least were sent to<lb/> me that my addressing a public body like yours<lb/> has the
                full approbation, consent and is in accordance</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>with the wishes of the gentlemen referred to in<lb/> their official capacity. There
                is ample<lb/> time yet to obtain this consent in writing before<lb/> the <date>12<hi
                        rend="sup">th</hi></date> proximo; and if not, or if <del>not, or if this
                        assert<add>?</add></del> it<lb/> cannot be obtained in a form and
                manner<lb/> recognized by me, there will be full opportunity<lb/> to select some
                person in my place who has<lb/> no such reason to refuse reluctantly
                com-<lb/>pliance, as I am compelled to do.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Have the goodness to inform me at your<lb/> earliest convenience of
                the determination<lb/> of your board, and accept in the mean-<lb/>while the
                assurance of my high regard.</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">Isaac Leeser</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName>
            </p>
            <p><date>January 24<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5616</date>.</p>
        </body>
